name: Apolline v2.0.0
body:
[Changelog] [PlayStore] 
  - Add auto launching synchronisation service (1 sync/h in WiFi only).
  - Add job persistance Android JobScheduler.
  - Add request disable Doze mode.
  - Add runtime permissions requests support for API < 26.
  - Add GeoHash support.
  - Add database migration.
  - Add CrashLytics and FireBase crash logs.
  - Add more export functions.
  - Fix some bugs.
